## 3. Core Value Propositions

### For Service Providers (Informal Workers)
- **Get discovered** by customers in their city who can't find them on any current platform
- **Get paid safely** with escrow protecting both parties
- **Build a financial identity** — every completed job adds to a verifiable credit score
- **Manage their business** from a dashboard — revenue, bookings, customer analytics
- **Unlock financial products** — the credit score opens doors to microloans, savings, and insurance in phase 2

### For Customers
- **Find verified, rated providers** near them using plain language search powered by AI
- **Book and pay safely** — money held in escrow until the job is confirmed complete
- **Trust the platform** — every provider is phone-verified with a behavioral track record

### For Financial Institutions (Phase 2 Partners)
- **Access a pre-scored population** of creditworthy informal workers with 6–24 months of behavioral data
- **No KYC cold start** — all users are phone-verified with an economic activity history
- **API access** to anonymised credit profiles for loan underwriting

