| **Radix UI Primitives** | Accessible components | Unstyled accessible primitives for modals, tabs, selects. Style with Tailwind. Avoids the complexity of full component libraries. |
| **Framer Motion** | Animations | Page transitions, score badge reveal animation, success states. Makes the demo feel polished. |

