## 14. All Screens — Frontend Design Specification

### Design Principles for the Designer

- **Mobile-first.** Design at 390px width (iPhone 14 base). Most Nigerian users will access on a phone via Chrome.
- **High contrast.** The primary color palette should work in direct sunlight.
- **Progressive disclosure.** Show the minimum needed on each screen. Don't overwhelm.
- **Currency formatting.** All amounts in ₦ with comma separators (₦1,200,000 not ₦1200000).
- **Score tier colors:** Bronze = #CD7F32, Silver = #A8A9AD, Gold = #FFD700, Platinum = #E5E4E2 on dark bg.

