## 18. Data Flow Diagrams

### User Registration & Wallet Creation

```
User submits form
      │
      ▼
POST /api/auth/register
      │
      ├── Zod validates body
      ├── Check phone not already registered (Prisma)
      ├── Create User record (Prisma)
      ├── Hash and store OTP in memory (TTL: 5 min)
      ├── Call Termii → send OTP SMS
      └── Return { message: "OTP sent" }

User submits OTP
      │
      ▼
POST /api/auth/verify-otp
      │
      ├── Match OTP against stored hash
      ├── Mark user.isVerified = true (Prisma)
      ├── Call Squad createVirtualAccount()
      ├── Store squadAccountNo + squadAccountRef on User (Prisma)
      ├── Sign JWT access token + refresh token
      └── Return { tokens, user, accountNumber }
```

### Booking Payment Flow

```
Customer books + pays
      │
      ▼
POST /api/bookings → creates PENDING booking
      │
Provider accepts
      │
      ▼
PATCH /api/bookings/:id/accept
      │
      ├── booking.service.js calls squad.payment.chargeWallet()
      ├── Squad charges customer's virtual account
      ├── Returns squadEscrowRef
      ├── Saves squadEscrowRef on booking
      ├── Booking status → ACCEPTED
      └── Notification sent to customer

Job completed
      │
      ▼
PATCH /api/bookings/:id/complete
      │
      ├── booking.service.js calls squad.transfer.transferToWallet()
      ├── Squad releases funds to provider wallet
      ├── Booking status → COMPLETED
      └── Squad fires webhook →

POST /api/webhooks/squad (transfer.success)
      │
      ├── HMAC signature verified
      ├── Transaction record created (Prisma)
      ├── provider.totalEarned += amount
      ├── provider.totalJobs += 1
      ├── scoring.service.computeScore(providerId)
      ├── provider.creditScore + provider.scoreTier updated
      ├── CreditScore snapshot saved
      ├── Notification: "₦X received for [service]"
      └── Termii SMS to provider
```

### AI Matching Flow

```
Customer types query
      │
      ▼
POST /api/ai/match { query, lat, lng, radius }
      │
      ├── Search Postgres: providers within radius (lat/lng math)
      ├── Filter: isAvailable = true, isVerified = true
      ├── Take top 15 by avgRating
      ├── Package provider summaries as JSON
      │
      ▼
Call Anthropic Claude API
  System prompt: matching engine instructions
  User message: { query, providers: [...] }
      │
      ▼
Claude returns ranked JSON array
  [{ id, rank, matchReason, confidence }, ...]
      │
      ├── Re-fetch full provider data for matched IDs from Postgres
      ├── Merge matchReason into each provider object
      └── Return sorted, enriched provider list to frontend
```

