## 22. MVP Scope — In vs Out

### In Scope (Build for Demo)

- Phone + OTP onboarding via Termii
- Optional NIN field (stored, not verified live)
- Provider and customer profile creation
- Squad virtual account auto-created on registration
- AI natural language search via Claude with match reasons displayed
- Service listing management (create, edit, pause, delete)
- Booking lifecycle (request → accept → complete)
- Squad escrow: charge on accept, release on complete
- Transaction history on both wallets
- Credit score badge computed from behavioral data
- Score updated via Squad webhook after every completed booking
- Provider analytics dashboard (revenue, jobs, customer geography, score history)
- AI business insights generated by Claude
- Post-job customer reviews
- Responsive web app (Next.js, mobile-first)
- Provider public profile page (SSR for SEO)
- In-app notifications

### Out of Scope (Phase 2)

- Live face scan / biometric verification (Smile Identity)
- Savings products and ROSCA groups
- Micro-insurance layer
- Micro-loan disbursement (score exists; loan product is phase 2)
- Mobile app (React Native)
- Redis caching layer
- Admin dashboard
- Dispute resolution beyond a "raise dispute" flag
- Multi-language support (phase 2 for rural expansion)

